name: [15/24] Secrets of Osaka - Night approached
description:
"The moon rises, the City starts breathing. What is this feeling? Why do we start breathing when it's dark?" 

Fifteenth picture of a 24 NFT Photography Adv(HEN)t Series. Secrets of Osaka's Sidealleys and Streets. Showing the exact coordinates of the Location the Photo was shot. We are only 9 left to go. We are steadily getting closer.
